SYNOPSIS
        string english_time(int iValue)

DESCRIPTION
        Returns a string conversion of the value iValue into the
        standard day/hour/minute/second format.

EXAMPLE
        write(english_time(10000)+"\n");
        Prints out: 2 hours, 46 minutes, and 40 seconds


SEE ALSO
        ctime(E), gmtime(E), localtime(E), utime(E)
